title: victorious ward not there?
body: i was just wondering why i didn't get the victorious ward but i did get the victorious graves reward is there something I'm missing?

replies.body: All of the ranked rewards haven't been delivered quite yet. They'll still be going out over the course of the month, and that victorious ward might just be delayed a little bit. If you still don't see yours in about a week or so make sure to shoot us a [**ticket**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).
